ossible</strong>, sans raccourci, sans réfléchir.</p>
<hr data-start="77" data-end="80">
<h3 data-start="82" data-end="128">✅ Solution qui marche à 100% (à la souris)</h3>
<ol data-start="130" data-end="292">
<li data-start="130" data-end="197">
<p data-start="133" data-end="197">En haut à gauche de VS Code<br data-start="160" data-end="163">
👉 clique sur les <strong data-start="181" data-end="197">3 traits (≡)</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="199" data-end="234">
<p data-start="202" data-end="234">Ensuite clique sur :<br>
👉 <strong data-start="226" data-end="234">View</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="236" data-end="263">
<p data-start="239" data-end="263">Puis :<br>
👉 <strong data-start="249" data-end="263">Appearance</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="265" data-end="292">
<p data-start="268" data-end="292">Puis :<br>
👉 <strong data-start="278" data-end="292">Reset Zoom</strong></p>
</li>
</ol>
<hr data-start="294" data-end="297">
<h3 data-start="299" data-end="339">🔴 Si tu ne trouves pas “Reset Zoom”</h3>
<p data-start="340" data-end="349">Fais ça :</p>
<ol data-start="351" data-end="590">
<li data-start="351" data-end="385">
<p data-start="354" data-end="385">Clique sur les <strong data-start="369" data-end="385">3 traits (≡)</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="386" data-end="413">
<p data-start="389" data-end="413">Clique sur :<br>
👉 <strong data-start="405" data-end="413">File</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="414" data-end="442">
<p data-start="417" data-end="442">Puis :<br>
👉 <strong data-start="427" data-end="442">Preferences</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="443" data-end="468">
<p data-start="446" data-end="468">Puis :<br>
👉 <strong data-start="456" data-end="468">Settings</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="470" data-end="526">
<p data-start="473" data-end="526">En haut, dans la barre de recherche :<br>
👉 écris <code data-start="520" data-end="526">zoom</code></p>
</li>
<li data-start="528" data-end="570">
<p data-start="531" data-end="570">Tu vas voir :<br>
👉 <strong data-start="548" data-end="570">Window: Zoom Level</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="572" data-end="590">
<p data-start="575" data-end="590">Mets :<br>
👉 <strong data-start="585" data-end="590">0</strong></p>
</li>
</ol>
<hr data-start="592" data-end="595">
<h3 data-start="597" data-end="642">⚠️ Important (très probable dans ton cas)</h3>
<p data-start="643" data-end="716">Vu ta capture → ça ressemble <strong data-start="672" data-end="702">beaucoup à un zoom Windows</strong>, pas VS Code.</p>
<p data-start="718" data-end="751">👉 Appuie sur :<br>
<strong data-start="734" data-end="751">Windows + Esc</strong></p>
<hr data-start="753" data-end="756">
<h3 data-start="758" data-end="783">💬 Dis-moi juste ça :</h3>
<p data-start="784" data-end="871">👉 Est-ce que <strong data-start="798" data-end="826">tout ton écran est zoomé</strong> (Chrome, tout)<br data-start="841" data-end="844">
OU<br data-start="846" data-end="849">
👉 seulement VS Code ?</p>
