<hr data-start="445" data-end="448">
<h2 data-start="450" data-end="474">✅ Ce que tu fais bien</h2>
<ul data-start="475" data-end="628">
<li data-start="475" data-end="498">
<p data-start="477" data-end="498">✔️ <code data-start="480" data-end="486">Link</code> → parfait</p>
</li>
<li data-start="499" data-end="547">
<p data-start="501" data-end="547">✔️ URL dynamique <code data-start="518" data-end="535">/logement/${id}</code> → parfait</p>
</li>
<li data-start="548" data-end="595">
<p data-start="550" data-end="595">✔️ props (<code data-start="560" data-end="564">id</code>, <code data-start="566" data-end="573">title</code>, <code data-start="575" data-end="582">cover</code>) → parfait</p>
</li>
<li data-start="596" data-end="628">
<p data-start="598" data-end="628">✔️ structure simple → nickel</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="630" data-end="679">👉 Franchement : <strong data-start="647" data-end="679">rien à corriger côté logique</strong></p>
<hr data-start="681" data-end="684">
<h2 data-start="686" data-end="720">🔥 Petit + (optionnel mais pro)</h2>
<p data-start="721" data-end="762">Tu peux ajouter une classe sur le titre :</p>
