ull"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼ5 ͼj"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span class="ͼ8">import</span><span> { </span><span class="ͼe">BrowserRouter</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼe">Routes</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼe">Route</span><span> } </span><span class="ͼ8">from</span><span> </span><span class="ͼc">"react-router-dom"</span><span>;</span><br><span class="ͼ8">import</span><span> </span><span class="ͼe">Home</span><span> </span><span class="ͼ8">from</span><span> </span><span class="ͼc">"./pages/Home/Home"</span><span>;</span><br><span class="ͼ8">import</span><span> </span><span class="ͼe">Logement</span><span> </span><span class="ͼ8">from</span><span> </span><span class="ͼc">"./pages/Logement/Logement"</span><span>;</span><br><span class="ͼ8">import</span><span> </span><span class="ͼe">Error</span><span> </span><span class="ͼ8">from</span><span> </span><span class="ͼc">"./pages/Error"</span><span>;</span><br><br><span class="ͼ8">function</span><span> </span><span class="ͼe">App</span><span>() {</span><br><span>  </span><span class="ͼ8">return</span><span> (</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼg">&lt;BrowserRouter&gt;</span><br><span>      </span><span class="ͼg">&lt;Routes&gt;</span><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼg">&lt;Route</span><span> </span><span class="ͼf">path</span><span class="ͼ8">=</span><span class="ͼc">"/"</span><span> </span><span class="ͼf">element</span><span class="ͼ8">=</span><span>{</span><span class="ͼg">&lt;Home</span><span> </span><span class="ͼg">/&gt;</span><span>} </span><span class="ͼg">/&gt;</span><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼg">&lt;Route</span><span> </span><span class="ͼf">path</span><span class="ͼ8">=</span><span class="ͼc">"/logement/:id"</span><span> </span><span class="ͼf">element</span><span class="ͼ8">=</span><span>{</span><span class="ͼg">&lt;Logement</span><span> </span><span class="ͼg">/&gt;</span><span>} </span><span class="ͼg">/&gt;</span><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼg">&lt;Route</span><span> </span><span class="ͼf">path</span><span class="ͼ8">=</span><span class="ͼc">"/error"</span><span> </span><span class="ͼf">element</span><span class="ͼ8">=</span><span>{</span><span class="ͼg">&lt;Error</span><span> </span><span class="ͼg">/&gt;</span><span>} </span><span class="ͼg">/&gt;</span><br><span>      </span><span class="ͼg">&lt;/Routes&gt;</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼg">&lt;/BrowserRouter&gt;</span><br><span>  );</span><br><span>}</span><br><br><span class="ͼ8">export</span><span> </span><span class="ͼ8">default</span><span> </span><span class="ͼe">App</span><span>;</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="1394" data-end="1397">
<h3 data-start="1399" data-end="1426">4. Ce que ça doit faire</h3>
<p data-start="1427" data-end="1459">Quand tu cliques sur une carte :</p>
<ul data-start="1460" data-end="1585">
<li data-start="1460" data-end="1497">
<p data-start="1462" data-end="1497"><code data-start="1462" data-end="1475">/logement/1</code> affiche le logement 1</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1498" data-end="1535">
<p data-start="1500" data-end="1535"><code data-start="1500" data-end="1513">/logement/2</code> affiche le logement 2</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1536" data-end="1585">
<p data-start="1538" data-end="1585">si l’id n’existe pas, redirection vers <code data-start="1577" data-end="1585">/error</code></p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="1587" data-end="1590">
<h3 data-start="1592" data-end="1611">5. Test à faire</h3>
