ll"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼ5 ͼj"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span class="ͼ8">import</span><span> { </span><span class="ͼe">Routes</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼe">Route</span><span> } </span><span class="ͼ8">from</span><span> </span><span class="ͼc">"react-router-dom"</span><span>;</span><br><span class="ͼ8">import</span><span> </span><span class="ͼe">Home</span><span> </span><span class="ͼ8">from</span><span> </span><span class="ͼc">"../pages/Home/Home"</span><span>;</span><br><span class="ͼ8">import</span><span> </span><span class="ͼe">About</span><span> </span><span class="ͼ8">from</span><span> </span><span class="ͼc">"../pages/About"</span><span>;</span><br><span class="ͼ8">import</span><span> </span><span class="ͼe">Error</span><span> </span><span class="ͼ8">from</span><span> </span><span class="ͼc">"../pages/Error"</span><span>;</span><br><span class="ͼ8">import</span><span> </span><span class="ͼe">Logement</span><span> </span><span class="ͼ8">from</span><span> </span><span class="ͼc">"../pages/Logement/Logement"</span><span>;</span><br><span class="ͼ8">import</span><span> </span><span class="ͼe">MainLayout</span><span> </span><span class="ͼ8">from</span><span> </span><span class="ͼc">"../layouts/MainLayout"</span><span>;</span><br><br><span class="ͼ8">export</span><span> </span><span class="ͼ8">default</span><span> </span><span class="ͼ8">function</span><span> </span><span class="ͼe">Router</span><span>() {</span><br><span>  </span><span class="ͼ8">return</span><span> (</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼg">&lt;Routes&gt;</span><br><span>      </span><span class="ͼg">&lt;Route</span><span> </span><span class="ͼf">element</span><span class="ͼ8">=</span><span>{</span><span class="ͼg">&lt;MainLayout</span><span> </span><span class="ͼg">/&gt;</span><span>}</span><span class="ͼg">&gt;</span><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼg">&lt;Route</span><span> </span><span class="ͼf">path</span><span class="ͼ8">=</span><span class="ͼc">"/"</span><span> </span><span class="ͼf">element</span><span class="ͼ8">=</span><span>{</span><span class="ͼg">&lt;Home</span><span> </span><span class="ͼg">/&gt;</span><span>} </span><span class="ͼg">/&gt;</span><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼg">&lt;Route</span><span> </span><span class="ͼf">path</span><span class="ͼ8">=</span><span class="ͼc">"/about"</span><span> </span><span class="ͼf">element</span><span class="ͼ8">=</span><span>{</span><span class="ͼg">&lt;About</span><span> </span><span class="ͼg">/&gt;</span><span>} </span><span class="ͼg">/&gt;</span><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼg">&lt;Route</span><span> </span><span class="ͼf">path</span><span class="ͼ8">=</span><span class="ͼc">"/logement/:id"</span><span> </span><span class="ͼf">element</span><span class="ͼ8">=</span><span>{</span><span class="ͼg">&lt;Logement</span><span> </span><span class="ͼg">/&gt;</span><span>} </span><span class="ͼg">/&gt;</span><br><span>      </span><span class="ͼg">&lt;/Route&gt;</span><br><span>      </span><span class="ͼg">&lt;Route</span><span> </span><span class="ͼf">path</span><span class="ͼ8">=</span><span class="ͼc">"*"</span><span> </span><span class="ͼf">element</span><span class="ͼ8">=</span><span>{</span><span class="ͼg">&lt;Error</span><span> </span><span class="ͼg">/&gt;</span><span>} </span><span class="ͼg">/&gt;</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼg">&lt;/Routes&gt;</span><br><span>  );</span><br><span>}</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<h3 data-start="845" data-end="889">2. Enregistre vraiment tous les fichiers</h3>
<p data-start="890" data-end="904">Dans VS Code :</p>
<ul data-start="905" data-end="926">
<li data-start="905" data-end="913">
<p data-start="907" data-end="913"><code data-start="907" data-end="913">File</code></p>
</li>
<li data-start="914" data-end="926">
<p data-start="916" data-end="926"><code data-start="916" data-end="926">Save All</code></p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="928" data-end="950">Ou avec le raccourci :</p>
<ul data-start="951" data-end="972">
<li data-start="951" data-end="972">
<p data-start="953" data-end="972"><code data-start="953" data-end="963">Ctrl + K</code> puis <code data-start="969" data-end="972">S</code></p>
</li>
</ul>
<h3 data-start="974" data-end="1003"><span role="text">3. Vérifie <code data-start="989" data-end="1003">Logement.jsx</code></span></h3>
<p data-start="1004" data-end="1033">Il faut bien ce fichier ici :</p>
<ul data-start="1034" data-end="1069">
<li data-start="1034" data-end="1069">
<p data-start="1036" data-end="1069"><code data-start="1036" data-end="1069">src/pages/Logement/Logement.jsx</code></p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="1071" data-end="1099">Avec exactement ce contenu :</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1101" data-end="1541"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="sticky z-2 select-none top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-cohbnghc.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>JavaScript</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copier" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-cohbnghc.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div></div></div><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-4 top-12 bottom-4"><div class="pointer-events-none sticky z-40 shrink-0 z-1!" style="top: calc(calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px) - 1px * 3); margin-bottom: calc(-4px); height: calc(4px); mask-image: linear-gradient(transparent 25%, white 75%);"><div class="sticky bg-token-border-light" style="top: calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px); height: 1px;"></div></div></div><div class="" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-