pan><span class="ͼg">&lt;h1&gt;</span><span>{</span><span class="ͼe">logement</span><span class="ͼ8">.</span><span>title}</span><span class="ͼg">&lt;/h1&gt;</span><br><span>      </span><span class="ͼg">&lt;img</span><span> </span><span class="ͼf">src</span><span class="ͼ8">=</span><span>{</span><span class="ͼe">logement</span><span class="ͼ8">.</span><span>cover} </span><span class="ͼf">alt</span><span class="ͼ8">=</span><span>{</span><span class="ͼe">logement</span><span class="ͼ8">.</span><span>title} </span><span class="ͼg">/&gt;</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼg">&lt;/main&gt;</span><br><span>  );</span><br><span>}</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<h3 data-start="1543" data-end="1579">4. Recharge complètement le site</h3>
<p data-start="1580" data-end="1600">Dans le navigateur :</p>
<ul data-start="1601" data-end="1625">
