<p data-start="1603" data-end="1625">appuie sur <code data-start="1614" data-end="1625">Ctrl + F5</code></p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="1627" data-end="1639">Puis teste :</p>
<ul data-start="1640" data-end="1676">
<li data-start="1640" data-end="1676">
<p data-start="1642" data-end="1676"><code data-start="1642" data-end="1676">http://localhost:5173/logement/1</code></p>
</li>
</ul>
<h3 data-start="1678" data-end="1709">5. Si ça affiche encore 404</h3>
