<h3 data-start="955" data-end="993">Ce qu’il faut vérifier sur ta home</h3>
<p data-start="994" data-end="1051">Ta page d’accueil doit avoir à peu près cette structure :</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1053" data-end="1330"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="sticky z-2 select-none top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-cohbnghc.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>JavaScript</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copier" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-cohbnghc.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div></div></div><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-4 top-12 bottom-4"><div class="pointer-events-none sticky z-40 shrink-0 z-1!" style="top: calc(calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px) - 1px * 3); margin-bottom: calc(-4px); height: calc(4px); mask-image: linear-gradient(transparent 25%, white 75%);"><div class="sticky bg-token-border-light" style="top: calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px); height: 1px;"></div></div></div><div class="" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼ5 ͼj"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span class="ͼg">&lt;main</span><span> </span><span class="ͼf">className</span><span class="ͼ8">=</span><span class="ͼc">"home"</span><span class="ͼg">&gt;</span><br><span>  </span><span class="ͼg">&lt;Banner</span><span> </span><span class="ͼg">/&gt;</span><br><span>  </span><span class="ͼg">&lt;section</span><span> </span><span class="ͼf">className</span><span class="ͼ8">=</span><span class="ͼc">"gallery"</span><span class="ͼg">&gt;</span><br><span>    {</span><span class="ͼe">logements</span><span class="ͼ8">.</span><span>map((</span><span class="ͼe">logement</span><span>) =&gt; (</span><br><span>      </span><span class="ͼg">&lt;Card</span><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼf">key</span><span class="ͼ8">=</span><span>{</span><span class="ͼe">logement</span><span class="ͼ8">.</span><span>id}</span><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼf">id</span><span class="ͼ8">=</span><span>{</span><span class="ͼe">logement</span><span class="ͼ8">.</span><span>id}</span><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼf">title</span><span class="ͼ8">=</span><span>{</span><span class="ͼe">logement</span><span class="ͼ8">.</span><span>title}</span><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼf">cover</span><span class="ͼ8">=</span><span>{</span><span class="ͼe">logement</span><span class="ͼ8">.</span><span>cover}</span><br><span>      </span><span class="ͼg">/&gt;</span><br><span>    ))}</span><br><span>  </span><span class="ͼg">&lt;/section&gt;</span><br><span class="ͼg">&lt;/main&gt;</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="1332" data-end="1335">
<h3 data-start="1337" data-end="1372">Et côté CSS, il faut au minimum</h3>
<p data-start="1373" data-end="1387">Pour <code data-start="1378" data-end="1385">.home</code> :</p>
<ul data-start="1388" data-end="1425">
<li data-start="1388" data-end="1401">
<p data-start="1390" data-end="1401">largeur max</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1402" data-end="1412">
<p data-start="1404" data-end="1412">centrage</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1413" data-end="1425">
<p data-start="1415" data-end="1425">marge auto</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="1427" data-end="1444">Pour <code data-start="1432" data-end="1442">.gallery</code> :</p>
<ul data-start="1445" data-end="1566">
<li data-start="1445" data-end="1462">
<p data-start="1447" data-end="1462"><code data-start="1447" data-end="1462">display: grid</code></p>
</li>
<li data-start="1463" data-end="1504">
<p data-start="1465" data-end="1504"><code data-start="1465" data-end="1504">grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr)</code></p>
</li>
<li data-start="1505" data-end="1512">
<p data-start="1507" data-end="1512"><code data-start="1507" data-end="1512">gap</code></p>
</li>
<li data-start="1513" data-end="1536">
<p data-start="1515" data-end="1536"><code data-start="1515" data-end="1536">background: #f6f6f6</code></p>
</li>
<li data-start="1537" data-end="1554">
<p data-start="1539" data-end="1554"><code data-start="1539" data-end="1554">border-radius</code></p>
</li>
<li data-start="1555" data-end="1566">
<p data-start="1557" data-end="1566"><code data-start="1557" data-end="1566">padding</code></p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="1568" data-end="1582">Pour <code data-start="1573" data-end="1580">.card</code> :</p>
<ul data-start="1583" data-end="1709">
<li data-start="1583" data-end="1597">
<p data-start="1585" data-end="1597">hauteur fixe</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1598" data-end="1620">
<p data-start="1600" data-end="1620"><code data-start="1600" data-end="1620">position: relative</code></p>
</li>
<li data-start="1621" data-end="1640">
<p data-start="1623" data-end="1640">image qui remplit</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1641" data-end="1668">
<p data-start="1643" data-end="1668">dégradé sombre par-dessus</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1669" data-end="1692">
<p data-start="1671" data-end="1692">titre en bas à gauche</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1693" data-end="1709">
<p data-start="1695" data-end="1709">coins arrondis</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="1711" data-end="1714">
<h3 data-start="1716" data-end="1728">En clair</h3>
<p data-start="1729" data-end="1855">Tu n’es pas encore à une home finalisée si elle ne ressemble pas à cette maquette.<br data-start="1811" data-end="1814">
Donc la bonne logique maintenant, c’est :</p>
<ol data-start="1857" data-end="1964">
<li data-start="1857" data-end="1887">
<p data-start="1860" data-end="1887">finir la <strong data-start="1869" data-end="1887">page d’accueil</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="1888" data-end="1926">
<p data-start="1891" data-end="1926">puis reprendre la <strong data-start="1909" data-end="1926">page logement</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="1927" data-end="1943">
<p data-start="1930" data-end="1943">puis carousel</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1944" data-end="1964">
<p data-start="1947" data-end="1964">puis finalisation</p>
</li>
</ol>
<p data-start="1966" data-end="2093" data-is-last-node="" data-is-only-node="">Envoie-moi maintenant le contenu de <strong data-start="2002" data-end="2016"><code data-start="2004" data-end="2014">Home.jsx</code></strong> et <strong data-start="2020" data-end="2034"><code data-start="2022" data-end="2032">home.css</code></strong>, et je te dirai exactement quoi modifier, ligne par ligne.</p></div></div></div></div><div class="z-0 flex min-h-[46px] justify-start"><div aria-label="Response actions" class="touch:-me-2 touch:-ms-3.5 -ms-2.5 -me-1 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-y-4 p-1 select-none touch:w-[calc(100%+--spacing(3.5))] -mt-1 w-[calc(100%+--spacing(2.5))] duration-[1.5s] focus-within:transition-none hover:transition-none touch:pointer-events-auto pointer-events-none [mask-image:linear-gradient(to_right,black_33%,transparent_66%)] [mask-size:300%_100%] [mask-position:100%_0%] motion-safe:transition-[mask-position] group-hover/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-hover/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] group-focus-within/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-focus-within/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] has-data-[state=open]:pointer-events-auto has-data-[state=open]:[mask-position:0_0]" role="group" tabindex="-1" style="mask-position: 0% 0%;"><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Copier la réponse" data-testid="copy-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-cohbnghc.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Bonne réponse" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="good-response-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-cohbnghc.svg#51753c" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Mauvaise réponse" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="bad-response-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-cohbnghc.svg#2126ae" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Partager" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-cohbnghc.svg#630ca2" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary touch:w-10 flex h-8 w-8 items-center justify-center rounded-lg" aria-label="Plus d’actions" type="button" id="radix-_r_2fe_" aria-haspopup="menu" aria-expanded="false" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-cohbnghc.svg#f6d0e2" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div></div></div></div><span class="sr-only"><br></span></section><section class="text-token-text-primary w-full focus:outline-none [--shadow-height:45px] has-data-writing-block:pointer-events-none has-data-writing-block:-mt-(--shadow-height) has-data-writing-block:pt-(--shadow-height) [&amp;:has([data-writing-block])&gt;*]:pointer-events-auto scroll-mt-(--header-height)" dir="auto" data-turn-id="7b3c1749-0d11-4cb2-a9d7-9a4e4e6245d5" data-testid="conversation-turn-49" data-scroll-anchor="false" data-turn="user"><h4 class="sr-only select-none">Vous avez dit&nbsp;:</h4><div class="text-base my-auto mx-auto pt-12 [--thread-content-margin:var(--thread-content-margin-xs,calc(var(--spacing)*4))] @w-sm/main:[--thread-content-margin:var(--thread-content-margin-sm,calc(var(--spacing)*6))] @w-lg/main:[--thread-content-margin:var(--thread-content-margin-lg,calc(var(--spacing)*16))] px-(--thread-content-margin)"><div class="[--thread-content-max-width:40rem] @w-lg/main:[--thread-content-max-width:48rem] mx-auto max-w-(--thread-content-max-width) flex-1 group/turn-messages focus-visible:outline-hidden relative flex w-full min-w-0 flex-col"><div class="flex max-w-full flex-col gap-4 grow"><div data-message-author-role="user" data-message-id="7b3c1749-0d11-4cb2-a9d7-9a4e4e6245d5" dir="auto" class="min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal outline-none keyboard-focused:focus-ring [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-1"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden items-end rtl:items-start"><div class="flex w-[var(--user-chat-width,70%)] flex-col items-end"><div class="flex flex-row items-center justify-end gap-1"><div class="overflow-hidden rounded-lg w-full h-full max-h-96 max-w-64"><div class="bg-token-main-surface-secondary text-token-text-tertiary relative flex h-auto w-full max-w-lg items-center justify-center overflow-hidden"><button type="button" aria-haspopup="dialog" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="radix-_r_2fh_" data-state="closed" class="overflow-hidden rounded-lg w-full h-full max-h-96 max-w-64" aria-label="Ouvrir l’image en plein écran"><img alt="Image chargée" width="536" height="614" loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="max-w-full object-cover object-center overflow-hidden rounded-lg w-full h-full max-h-96 max-w-64 w-fit transition-opacity duration-300 opacity-100" src="./banner_files/ca2f37d7-156b-4c20-8116-190bd3d77f6c.png"></button></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="text-token-text-secondary my-2 me-4 flex flex-row justify-end gap-1 text-xs"></div></div><div class="z-0 flex justify-end"><div aria-label="Your message actions" class="touch:-me-2 touch:-ms-3.5 -ms-2.5 -me-1 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-y-4 p-1 select-none focus-within:transition-none hover:transition-none touch:pointer-events-auto touch:opacity-100 duration-300 group-hover/turn-messages:delay-300 pointer-events-none opacity-0 motion-safe:transition-opacity group-hover/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-hover/turn-messages:opacity-100 group-focus-within/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-focus-within/turn-messages:opacity-100 has-data-[state=open]:pointer-events-auto has-data-[state=open]:opacity-100" role="group" tabindex="-1" style="mask-position: 0% 0%;"><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Copier le message" data-testid="copy-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-cohbnghc.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button></div></div></div></div><span class="sr-only"><br></span></section><section class="text-token-text-primary w-full focus:outline-none [--shadow-height:45px] has-data-writing-block:pointer-events-none has-data-writing-block:-mt-(--shadow-height) has-data-writing-block:pt-(--shadow-height) [&amp;:has([data-writing-block])&gt;*]:pointer-events-auto scroll-mt-[calc(var(--header-height)+min(200px,max(70px,20svh)))]" dir="auto" data-turn-id="request-WEB:1df6e033-48f7-4a7c-9a2d-b8fbb1350489-24" data-testid="conversation-turn-50" data-scroll-anchor="false" data-turn="assistant"><h4 class="sr-only select-none">ChatGPT a dit&nbsp;:</h4><div class="text-base my-auto mx-auto [--thread-content-margin:var(--thread-content-margin-xs,calc(var(--spacing)*4))] @w-sm/main:[--thread-content-margin:var(--thread-content-margin-sm,calc(var(--spacing)*6))] @w-lg/main:[--thread-content-margin:var(--thread-content-margin-lg,calc(var(--spacing)*16))] px-(--thread-content-margin)"><div class="[--thread-content-max-width:40rem] @w-lg/main:[--thread-content-max-width:48rem] mx-auto max-w-(--thread-content-max-width) flex-1 group/turn-messages focus-visible:outline-hidden relative flex w-full min-w-0 flex-col agent-turn"><div class="flex max-w-full flex-col gap-4 grow"><div data-message-author-role="assistant" data-message-id="db33c26b-9314-47cb-a0f8-7a3a8844d28d" dir="auto" data-message-model-slug="gpt-5-4-thinking" class="min-h-8 text-message relative flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 text-start break-words whitespace-normal outline-none keyboard-focused:focus-ring [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-1"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden"><div class="markdown prose dark:prose-invert w-full wrap-break-word light markdown-new-styling"><p data-start="0" data-end="56">Oui, cette capture précise bien la logique de l’étape 4.</p>
<h3 data-start="58" data-end="95">Ce que l’étape 4 demande vraiment</h3>
<p data-start="96" data-end="136">À la fin de cette étape, tu dois avoir :</p>
<ul data-start="138" data-end="280">
<li data-start="138" data-end="183">
<p data-start="140" data-end="183">les composants <strong data-start="155" data-end="165">Banner</strong> et <strong data-start="169" data-end="177">Card</strong> créés</p>
</li>
<li data-start="184" data-end="217">
<p data-start="186" data-end="217">la <strong data-start="189" data-end="217">récupération des données</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="218" data-end="280">
<p data-start="220" data-end="280">la <strong data-start="223" data-end="259">liste des propriétés disponibles</strong> affichée sur la home</p>
</li>
</ul>
<h3 data-start="282" data-end="323">Donc, par rapport à ton projet actuel</h3>
<p data-start="324" data-end="336">Tu as déjà :</p>
<ul data-start="337" data-end="464">
<li data-start="337" data-end="361">
<p data-start="339" data-end="361">le routage fonctionnel</p>
</li>
<li data-start="362" data-end="377">
<p data-start="364" data-end="377"><code data-start="364" data-end="372">Banner</code> créé</p>
</li>
<li data-start="378" data-end="391">
<p data-start="380" data-end="391"><code data-start="380" data-end="386">Card</code> créé</p>
</li>
<li data-start="392" data-end="440">
<p data-start="394" data-end="440">une liste de logements affichable via ton JSON</p>
</li>
<li data-start="441" data-end="464">
<p data-start="443" data-end="464">des cartes cliquables</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="466" data-end="556">Donc sur le <strong data-start="478" data-end="493">fonctionnel</strong>, tu es déjà <strong data-start="506" data-end="540">au moins à la fin de l’étape 4</strong>, voire au-delà.</p>
<h3 data-start="558" data-end="576">Mais attention</h3>
<p data-start="577" data-end="604">La capture parle aussi de :</p>
<ul data-start="605" data-end="727">
<li data-start="605" data-end="643">
<p data-start="607" data-end="643">récupération des données du back-end</p>
</li>
<li data-start="644" data-end="685">
<p data-start="646" data-end="685">éventuellement <code data-start="661" data-end="671">useState</code> / <code data-start="674" data-end="685">useEffect</code></p>
</li>
<li data-start="686" data-end="727">
<p data-start="688" data-end="727">API sur <code data-start="696" data-end="727">localhost:8080/api/properties</code></p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="729" data-end="803">Or toi, actuellement, tu utilises un <strong data-start="766" data-end="788">fichier JSON local</strong> dans <code data-start="794" data-end="802">assets</code>.</p>
<h3 data-start="805" data-end="826">Conclusion claire</h3>
<p data-start="827" data-end="834">Tu es :</p>
<ul data-start="836" data-end="1148">
<li data-start="836" data-end="913">
<p data-start="838" data-end="913"><strong data-start="838" data-end="854">visuellement</strong> : ta home n’est pas encore totalement fidèle à la maquette</p>
</li>
<li data-start="914" data-end="982">
<p data-start="916" data-end="982"><strong data-start="916" data-end="937">fonctionnellement</strong> : tu as déjà validé l’essentiel de l’étape 4</p>
</li>
<li data-start="983" data-end="1148">
<p data-start="985" data-end="1148"><strong data-start="985" data-end="1029">par rapport aux consignes OpenClassrooms</strong> : il faut vérifier si on attend de toi une vraie récupération API ou si le JSON local suffit dans ta version du projet</p>
</li>
</ul>
<h3 data-start="1150" data-end="1182">Le plus important maintenant</h3>
<p data-start="1183" data-end="1234">Avant d’avancer encore, il faut trancher ce point :</p>
<p data-start="1236" data-end="1377"><strong data-start="1236" data-end="1377">Est-ce que ton mentor t’a demandé d’utiliser les vraies données de l’API/back-end, ou juste les vraies données Kasa dans un JSON fourni ?</strong></p>
<p data-start="1379" data-end="1390">Parce que :</p>
<ul data-start="1391" data-end="1562">
<li data-start="1391" data-end="1475">
<p data-start="1393" data-end="1475">si c’est <strong data-start="1402" data-end="1409">API</strong> → on revient sur l’étape 4 proprement avec <code data-start="1453" data-end="1464">useEffect</code> et <code data-start="1468" data-end="1475">fetch</code></p>
</li>
<li data-start="1476" data-end="1562">
<p data-start="1478" data-end="1562">si c’est <strong data-start="1487" data-end="1502">JSON fourni</strong> → on peut continuer sur la mise en page et la page logement</p>
</li>
</ul>
