</li>
</ul>
<h3 data-start="844" data-end="887"><span role="text">3. Ajoute un petit test dans <code data-start="877" data-end="887">Home.jsx</code></span></h3>
<p data-start="888" data-end="967">Remplace temporairement ton <code data-start="916" data-end="927">useEffect</code> par ça pour voir ce que l’API renvoie :</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="969" data-end="1249"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="sticky z-2 select-none top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-cohbnghc.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>JavaScript</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copier" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-cohbnghc.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div></div></div><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-4 top-12 bottom-4"><div class="pointer-events-none sticky z-40 shrink-0 z-1!" style="top: calc(calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px) - 1px * 3); margin-bottom: calc(-4px); height: calc(4px); mask-image: linear-gradient(transparent 25%, white 75%);"><div class="sticky bg-token-border-light" style="top: calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px); height: 1px;"></div></div></div><div class="" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼ5 ͼj"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span class="ͼe">useEffect</span><span>(() =&gt; {</span><br><span>  </span><span class="ͼe">fetch</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼc">"http://localhost:8080/api/properties"</span><span>)</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼ8">.</span><span>then((</span><span class="ͼe">response</span><span>) =&gt; </span><span class="ͼe">response</span><span class="ͼ8">.</span><span>json())</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼ8">.</span><span>then((</span><span class="ͼe">data</span><span>) =&gt; {</span><br><span>      </span><span class="ͼe">console</span><span class="ͼ8">.</span><span>log(</span><span class="ͼc">"DATA API :"</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼe">data</span><span>);</span><br><span>      </span><span class="ͼe">setLogements</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼe">data</span><span>);</span><br><span>    })</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼ8">.</span><span>catch((</span><span class="ͼe">error</span><span>) =&gt; </span><span class="ͼe">console</span><span class="ͼ8">.</span><span>error(</span><span class="ͼc">"ERREUR API :"</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼe">error</span><span>));</span><br><span>}, []);</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="1251" data-end="1257">Puis :</p>
<ul data-start="1258" data-end="1356">
<li data-start="1258" data-end="1270">
<p data-start="1260" data-end="1270">enregistre</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1271" data-end="1289">
<p data-start="1273" data-end="1289">recharge la page</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1290" data-end="1310">
<p data-start="1292" data-end="1310">va dans la console</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1311" data-end="1356">
<p data-start="1313" data-end="1356">regarde ce qui s’affiche après <code data-start="1344" data-end="1356">DATA API :</code></p>
</li>
</ul>
<h3 data-start="1358" data-end="1410">4. Vérifie aussi que ton rendu est bien comme ça</h3>
<p data-start="1411" data-end="1458">Dans <code data-start="1416" data-end="1426">Home.jsx</code>, la partie retour doit rester :</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1460" data-end="1775"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="sticky z-2 select-none top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-cohbnghc.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>JavaScript</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copier" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-cohbnghc.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div></div></div><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-4 top-12 bottom-4"><div class="pointer-events-none sticky z-40 shrink-0 z-1!" style="top: calc(calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px) - 1px * 3); margin-bottom: calc(-4px); height: calc(4px); mask-image: linear-gradient(transparent 25%, white 75%);"><div class="sticky bg-token-border-light" style="top: calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px); height: 1px;"></div></div></div><div class="" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼ5 ͼj"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span class="ͼ8">return</span><span> (</span><br><span>  </span><span class="ͼg">&lt;main</span><span> </span><span class="ͼf">className</span><span class="ͼ8">=</span><span class="ͼc">"home"</span><span class="ͼg">&gt;</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼg">&lt;Banner</span><span> </span><span class="ͼg">/&gt;</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼg">&lt;section</span><span> </span><span class="ͼf">className</span><span class="ͼ8">=</span><span class="ͼc">"gallery"</span><span class="ͼg">&gt;</span><br><span>      {</span><span class="ͼe">logements</span><span class="ͼ8">.</span><span>map((</span><span class="ͼe">logement</span><span>) =&gt; (</span><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼg">&lt;Card</span><br><span>          </span><span class="ͼf">key</span><span class="ͼ8">=</span><span>{</span><span class="ͼe">logement</span><span class="ͼ8">.</span><span>id}</span><br><span>          </span><span class="ͼf">id</span><span class="ͼ8">=</span><span>{</span><span class="ͼe">logement</span><span class="ͼ8">.</span><span>id}</span><br><span>          </span><span class="ͼf">title</span><span class="ͼ8">=</span><span>{</span><span class="ͼe">logement</span><span class="ͼ8">.</span><span>title}</span><br><span>          </span><span class="ͼf">cover</span><span class="ͼ8">=</span><span>{</span><span class="ͼe">logement</span><span class="ͼ8">.</span><span>cover}</span><br><span>        </span><span class="ͼg">/&gt;</span><br><span>      ))}</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼg">&lt;/section&gt;</span><br><span>  </span><span class="ͼg">&lt;/main&gt;</span><br><span>);</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<h3 data-start="1777" data-end="1806">5. Cause la plus probable</h3>
<p data-start="1807" data-end="1982">Le plus probable, c’est que le back-end n’est pas démarré.<br data-start="1865" data-end="1868">
Comme ton mentor a parlé d’une API en <code data-start="1906" data-end="1922">localhost:8080</code>, il faut souvent lancer un serveur séparé en plus du front.</p>
<p data-start="1984" data-end="2145" data-is-last-node="" data-is-only-node="">Donc là, j’ai besoin d’une seule info pour te débloquer :<br>
<strong data-start="2042" data-end="2145" data-is-last-node="">qu’est-ce qui s’affiche quand tu ouvres <code data-start="2084" data-end="2122">http://localhost:8080/api/properties</code> dans le navigateur ?</strong></p></div></div></div></div><div class="z-0 flex min-h-[46px] justify-start"><div aria-label="Response actions" class="touch:-me-2 touch:-ms-3.5 -ms-2.5 -me-1 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-y-4 p-1 select-none touch:w-[calc(100%+--spacing(3.5))] -mt-1 w-[calc(100%+--spacing(2.5))] duration-[1.5s] focus-within:transition-none hover:transition-none touch:pointer-events-auto pointer-events-none [mask-image:linear-gradient(to_right,black_33%,transparent_66%)] [mask-size:300%_100%] [mask-position:100%_0%] motion-safe:transition-[mask-position] group-hover/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-hover/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] group-focus-within/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-focus-within/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] has-data-[state=open]:pointer-events-auto has-data-[state=open]:[mask-position:0_0]" role="group" tabindex="-1" style="mask-position: 0% 0%;"><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Copier la réponse" data-testid="copy-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-cohbnghc.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Bonne réponse" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="good-response-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-cohbnghc.svg#51753c" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button>