<p data-start="3019" data-end="3043">cartes en grille dessous</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="3045" data-end="3220" data-is-last-node="" data-is-only-node="">Le vrai point bloquant maintenant, c’est surtout <strong data-start="3094" data-end="3111">le logo image</strong>.<br data-start="3112" data-end="3115">
