<h2 data-start="12" data-end="24">Étape 2</h2>
<p data-start="25" data-end="72">Maintenant, ajoute les images dans ce dossier :</p>
<p data-start="74" data-end="102">Dans <code data-start="79" data-end="94">public/images</code>, mets :</p>
<ul data-start="103" data-end="159">
<li data-start="103" data-end="127">
<p data-start="105" data-end="127">un logo → <strong data-start="115" data-end="127">logo.png</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="128" data-end="159">
<p data-start="130" data-end="159">une bannière → <strong data-start="145" data-end="159">banner.png</strong></p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="161" data-end="173">👉 Tu peux :</p>
<ul data-start="174" data-end="290">
<li data-start="174" data-end="216">
<p data-start="176" data-end="216">soit les glisser-déposer depuis ton PC</p>
</li>
<li data-start="217" data-end="290">
<p data-start="219" data-end="237">soit télécharger :</p>
<ul data-start="240" data-end="290">
<li data-start="240" data-end="251">
<p data-start="242" data-end="251">logo Kasa</p>
</li>
<li data-start="254" data-end="290">
<p data-start="256" data-end="290">bannière Kasa (celle avec paysage)</p>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="292" data-end="306">⚠️ Important :</p>
<ul data-start="307" data-end="349">
<li data-start="307" data-end="349">
<p data-start="309" data-end="349">noms EXACTS → <code data-start="323" data-end="333">logo.png</code> et <code data-start="337" data-end="349">banner.png</code></p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="351" data-end="354">
